Here are FHIR queries to find patients on prostate cancer drugs, covering the major drug classes (androgen receptor antagonists, CYP17 inhibitors, GnRH agonists/antagonists):

```
// Enzalutamide (Xtandi) - AR antagonist
MedicationRequest?code=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|1307058&status=active&_include=MedicationRequest:patient

// Apalutamide (Erleada) - AR antagonist
MedicationRequest?code=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|1946841&status=active&_include=MedicationRequest:patient

// Darolutamide (Nubeqa) - AR antagonist
MedicationRequest?code=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|2169313&status=active&_include=MedicationRequest:patient

// Bicalutamide (Casodex) - AR antagonist
MedicationRequest?code=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|149462&status=active&_include=MedicationRequest:patient

// Abiraterone (Zytiga) - CYP17 inhibitor
MedicationRequest?code=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|1100076&status=active&_include=MedicationRequest:patient

// Degarelix (Firmagon) - GnRH antagonist
MedicationRequest?code=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|727097&status=active&_include=MedicationRequest:patient

// Relugolix (Orgovyx) - GnRH antagonist
MedicationRequest?code=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|2200664&status=active&_include=MedicationRequest:patient

// Leuprolide (Lupron) - GnRH agonist
MedicationRequest?code=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|203923&status=active&_include=MedicationRequest:patient

// Goserelin (Zoladex) - GnRH agonist
MedicationRequest?code=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|41493&status=active&_include=MedicationRequest:patient

// Flutamide - AR antagonist (older generation)
MedicationRequest?code=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|4103&status=active&_include=MedicationRequest:patient

// Nilutamide - AR antagonist (older generation)
MedicationRequest?code=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|72179&status=active&_include=MedicationRequest:patient

// Cabazitaxel (Jevtana) - chemotherapy for mCRPC
MedicationRequest?code=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|1043427&status=active&_include=MedicationRequest:patient
```

**Notes:**
- `status=active` filters for currently prescribed medications
- `_include=MedicationRequest:patient` pulls back the associated Patient resources
- You can also cross-reference using the prostate cancer diagnosis:
  - `Condition?code=http://hl7.org/fhir/sid/icd-10-cm|C61&_include=Condition:patient` (malignant neoplasm of prostate)
  - `Condition?code=http://snomed.info/sct|399068003&_include=Condition:patient`
- Consider also querying `MedicationStatement` with the same codes if medication history (not just prescriptions) is needed.
